data.description: Incredible opportunity to own a large 5-acre family home less than a hour from INTEL. This all-brick home sitting on 5 acres has 3 full bedrooms, 1 full and 1 half bath with a large open concept kitchen and dining room with a fireplace. Large living room with fireplace for entertaining for the Holidays. Just off the foyer is a family room that can be used as an office or formal dining room. Large primary bedroom will hold a king size bed and have room for a sitting area as well as 2 additional bedrooms and family bath. Located in the walkout basement are 3 large rooms, 2 currently used as bedrooms, a play area and a utility room. Pellet stove to heat the home should you lose power. Detached 2 car garage to keep your cars out of the elements as well as a enclosed porch to dry the dogs off and drop your boots. This 5-acres partially wooded lot is a great place to raise a family in a rural setting and still be close to all the amenities of Columbus.
